{
  "text": "I understand that the Logos did not plan for the heating effect that occurs in our third-density transition into fourth. Is this correct? I am Ra. This is correct except for the condition of free will which is, of course, planned by the Logos as It, Itself, is a creature of free will. In this climate an infinity of events or conditions may occur. They cannot be said to be planned by the Logos but can be said to have been freely allowed.",
